00:25:18.230 --> 00:25:22.510
about a soundscape that is
extremely rich and diverse.

00:25:22.510 --> 00:25:30.510
And one in which there are clearly
are no walls, but lots of moments

00:25:30.510 --> 00:25:34.430
of blending and crossover
between communities.

00:25:34.430 --> 00:25:44.360 position:56%
So, if we can take ourselves for a
moment and imagine the unseen world,

00:25:44.360 --> 00:25:47.410
which of course is the
world of sound, right,

00:25:47.410 --> 00:25:51.170
