01:03:26.520 --> 01:03:31.880 position:56%
An additional Jewish ethnic identity
becomes truly diasporic only

01:03:31.880 --> 01:03:34.970
when a robust consciousness
of another homeland,

01:03:34.970 --> 01:03:38.350
in addition to ancient Israel,
as well as a sense of belonging

01:03:38.350 --> 01:03:40.390
to another transnation in addition

01:03:40.390 --> 01:03:43.530
to the transnational Jewish
community, are maintained

01:03:43.530 --> 01:03:46.030
through cultural expressions
of the community.

01:03:46.030 --> 01:03:49.200
Moroccan Jews in America
rely upon musical expressions

01:03:49.200 --> 01:03:51.720
in the synagogue life
to construct dimensions

01:03:51.720 --> 01:03:54.830
of what I call a Layered
Diaspora Consciousness.

01:03:54.830 --> 01:03:56.800
Connoting the complex juxtaposition

01:03:56.800 --> 01:04:00.770
of multiple Jewish diasporic
ethnic identities informing,

01:04:00.770 --> 01:04:05.180
a Layered Diaspora Consciousness is
a term used to describe how members

01:04:05.180 --> 01:04:08.530
of the American Moroccan
Jewish community use forms

01:04:08.530 --> 01:04:13.350
of musical expression to reproduce,
reinterpret, and transmit traits

01:04:13.350 --> 01:04:14.700
from three overlapping

01:04:14.700 --> 01:04:18.650
yet distinctive diasporic
ethnic identities: Jewish,

01:04:18.650 --> 01:04:22.100
Shephardi (Spanish),
and Maroka'i, Moroccan.

01:04:22.100 --> 01:04:26.100
I envision this Layered Diaspora
Consciousness as an amalgamation

01:04:26.100 --> 01:04:29.000
of different diasporic
ethnic identities

01:04:29.000 --> 01:04:32.490
and these layers should not be
seen as hierarchical or nesting,

01:04:32.490 --> 01:04:36.040
but rather they are
interacting rather than competing

01:04:36.040 --> 01:04:41.070
with one another, a co-mingling
of Diaspora identities.

01:04:41.070 --> 01:04:45.520
As a dynamic cultural expression,
music has a privileged role

01:04:45.520 --> 01:04:48.700
in affecting this Layered
Diaspora Consciousness.

01:04:48.700 --> 01:04:52.610
Music is a dynamic medium
that engages with the past

01:04:52.610 --> 01:04:54.650
and present simultaneously,

01:04:54.650 --> 01:04:57.480
and is used to convey
communal narrative histories

01:04:57.480 --> 01:05:01.130
and negotiate communal
boundaries and cultural influences.

01:05:01.130 --> 01:05:04.360
Musical expression has a
specialized role in the life

01:05:04.360 --> 01:05:06.720
of the Moroccan American
Jewish community.

01:05:06.720 --> 01:05:10.580
It is the preferred medium for
