01:12:22.920 --> 01:12:28.980
And-- I guess two parts
to this question --

01:12:28.980 --> 01:12:30.430
have they maintained that language?

01:12:30.430 --> 01:12:33.900
And what has happened to the
Moroccans who moved to Israel?

01:12:33.900 --> 01:12:40.330
Have they maintained the
languages that they were speaking

01:12:40.330 --> 01:12:42.450
to each other in Morocco?

01:12:42.450 --> 01:12:47.560
&gt;&gt; Samuel Thomas: And I want to
expand the notion of language

01:12:47.560 --> 01:12:50.510
