whether it'd be songs

01:14:15.880 --> 01:14:18.140
at a wedding even or a
circumcision ceremony

01:14:18.140 --> 01:14:22.090
or Haylula celebration are these
kinds of areas allow for this

01:14:22.090 --> 01:14:24.050
to be continued and sort of
encoded over generations.

